14:31:53.628 [INFO]   - `queue_target: vault2`
14:31:53.628 [INFO] - Treat the requested file set as one migration batch, even if it contains only one file:
14:31:53.628 [INFO]   - capture the current UTC timestamp once for the batch and write that same RFC3339 `queue_batch_timestamp` to every touched file, using the `Z` form like `2026-04-10T14:37:12Z`
14:31:53.628 [INFO]   - sort the requested file paths alphanumerically and assign `queue_order_id` from `1` through `N` in that order
